Class CssPropertySignature

java.lang.Object
  com.google.caja.parser.css.CssPropertySignature
All Implemented Interfaces:
ParseTreeNode, MessagePart, Renderable, java.lang.Cloneable
Direct Known Subclasses:
CssPropertySignature.CallSignature, CssPropertySignature.LiteralSignature, CssPropertySignature.PropertyRefSignature, CssPropertySignature.RepeatedSignature, CssPropertySignature.SeriesSignature, CssPropertySignature.SetSignature, CssPropertySignature.SymbolSignature
public abstract class CssPropertySignature
extends java.lang.Object
implements ParseTreeNode

A description of the values that can occur after a property.

See the value description language from http://www.w3.org/TR/CSS21/about.html#property-defs

Author:
mikesamuel@gmail.com
